<section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
                <div class="faq-title text-center pb-3">
                    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <div class="faq" id="accordion">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="faqHeading-1">
                            <div class="mb-0">
                                <h5 class="faq-title" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faqCollapse-1" data-area-expanded="true" data-area-controls="faqCollapse-1">
                                    <p>How do I start the buying process?</p>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="faqCollapse-1" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading-1" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>You can start by browsing our extensive listings to discover properties that match your preferences and needs.</p>
                                <p> 
                                    While optional, we recommend partnering with a property agent on our website to facilitate a smoother process. 
                                    They can offer valuable insights and guidance every step of the way.
                                </p>
                                <p>Once you’ve found a property you’re interested in, either you or your agent can reach out to the seller to negotiate the price and arrange viewings.</p>
                                <p>If you’re satisfied with the property and terms, proceed with the purchase to make the property yours.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="faqHeading-2">
                            <div class="mb-0">
                                <h5 class="faq-title" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faqCollapse-2" data-area-expanded="true" data-area-controls="faqCollapse-2">
                                    <p>What are the additional costs involved in purchasing a property?</p>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="faqCollapse-2" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading-2" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                When purchasing a property through our marketplace, buyers can rejoice in the fact that there are no additional fees charged by us. 
                                The seller is responsible for a 2% fee on the base price of the property, ensuring a transparent and buyer-friendly transaction. 
                                Please note that while our platform does not impose any extra charges on buyers, standard property purchasing costs such as stamp duty, legal fees, and mortgage-related expenses still apply and are handled by the seller.
                            </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="faqHeading-3">
                            <div class="mb-0">
                                <h5 class="faq-title" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faqCollapse-3" data-area-expanded="true" data-area-controls="faqCollapse-3">
                                    <p>How can I list a property on Sigma Properties?</p>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="faqCollapse-3" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading-3" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                First, create a Sigma Properties account as a seller. Then click on list properties in the navbar and fill in the details.
                                After submitting, give 3 working days for our staff to check the listing and approve it.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
